| f/1,4 || f/2 || f/2,8 || f/4 || f/5,6 || f/8 || f/11 || f/16 || f/22 || f/32
|-
! style="text-align: left" | Diamètre
| ''d'' || ''d''/√2 || ''d''/2 || ''d''/2√2 || ''d''/4 || ''d''/4√2 || ''d''/8 || ''d''/8√2 || ''d''/16 || ''d''/16√2
|-
